at nothing to exact his revenge.

00:21:27.328 --> 00:21:28.455 position:50% align:center
That's scary.

00:21:28.538 --> 00:21:29.664 position:50% align:center
[EDMUND]
You knew Five?

00:21:29.748 --> 00:21:32.000 position:50% align:center
Stop yankin' my chain.

00:21:32.083 --> 00:21:33.752 position:50% align:center
[JUZO]
I remember him.

00:21:33.835 --> 00:21:35.670 position:50% align:center
We have history.

00:21:35.754 --> 00:21:37.547 position:50% align:center
[EDMUND]
Have you seen him lately?

00:21:37.630 --> 00:21:39.716 position:50% align:center
