00:21:39.799 --> 00:21:42.427 position:50% align:center
I can't sleep until he's dead!

00:21:45.472 --> 00:21:47.557 position:50% align:center
[JUZO]
Then I've got news for you.

00:21:48.600 --> 00:21:50.310 position:50% align:center
[JUZO]
You can rest easy.

00:21:50.393 --> 00:21:51.895 position:50% align:center
'Cause six years ago,

00:21:51.978 --> 00:21:55.774 position:50% align:center
I took care of him
with my own two hands.

00:23:27.824 --> 00:23:29.200 position:50% align:center
[TETSURO]
Juzo.

00:23:29.284 --> 00:23:30.869 position:50% align:center
You're always fighting for
someone other than yourself.

00:23:30.952 --> 00:23:32.203 position:50% align:center
[EDMUND]
Why did you murder my partner?

00:23:32.287 --> 00:23:35.582 position:50% align:center
